 Omimas E-Commerce Project - Technical Details
ğŸ“‹ Project Summary
Omimas is a fully functional e-commerce platform targeting the Polish market. It offers a modern shopping experience similar to Allegro.

ğŸ› ï¸ Technologies Used
Backend:
Python 3.12 - Main programming language

Flask 2.3.3 - Web framework

Flask-SQLAlchemy 3.0.5 - ORM and database management

SQLite - Database (for development environment)

Werkzeug - Password hashing and security

Frontend:
HTML5 - Page structure

CSS3 - Design and responsive layout

JavaScript - Dynamic functions

Jinja2 - Template engine

Font Awesome 6 - Icons

API Integrations:
DummyJSON API - For product data

RESTful API - Our own backend APIs

ğŸ—ƒï¸ Database Structure
Models:
User - User information and authentication

Product - Product catalog and details

Category - Category management

Cart - Shopping cart operations

Order - Order management

OrderItem - Order details

Review - Product review and rating system

ShippingTracking - Shipping tracking system

ğŸŒ Data Sources
1. Product Data
Source: DummyJSON API (https://dummyjson.com/products)

Method: REST API GET request

Process: Data from API is automatically saved to SQLite database

Conversion: USD prices converted to PLN (1 USD = 4 PLN)

2. Category Data
Source: Manually defined (20+ categories)

Structure: Smartphones, Laptops, Fragrances, Skincare, Groceries, etc.

3. User Data
Source: User registration form

Security: Passwords stored as hashes

